This is the second stable release of Hastymail2. This release brings a few new
features and updates to the stable series but mostly fixes for user reported
issues. The full list of changes in this release can be found in the CHANGES
file in the download or online at:

http://hastymail.svn.sourceforge.net/viewvc/hastymail/trunk/hastymail2/CHANGES?view=markup

Thanks to everyone for your support. We value all feedback and comments so if
you are interested in helping with the Hastymail project you can find many ways
to get in touch with us at the contact page of our website:

http://www.hastymail.org/contact_us/

Jason Munro
jason@hastymail.org
